  "text": "On the other hand, we found no evidence of this problem for EDTA-derivatized DNA, presumably because the EDTA group is conjugated through a stable linker without a disulfide bond [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The SRY/DNA complex containing dT-EDTA-Mn 2+ exhibited the same 1 H N -C 2 values within experimental errors even 2 years after the first measurement (data not shown).",
